{"tid":1019934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本「胸罩日」　寫真女星紛紛秀美乳照","createTime":"2019-02-13T09:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T13:19:35.000Z","uid":75969,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0aad3655d8bb49bb9e8006f74f4df9659ce0940","tid":1019934,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190213/640_f75f95dd22b9cf88e7fea6a2b6fe95ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190213%2F640_f75f95dd22b9cf88e7fea6a2b6fe95ce.jpg&h=6031ce3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自森咲智美推特<br />\n<br />\n2月12日是「胸罩日」，不少日本寫真女星都在《推特》分享巨乳照跟粉絲互動。<br />\n<br />\n1913年，美國一名女子瑪麗&middot;菲爾普斯&middot;雅各布(Mary Phelps Jacobs)使用了手帕跟緞帶，發明了胸罩的原型，而在隔年2月12日申請專利，於是2月12日就成為了胸罩日。為了響應這個節日，日本許多寫真女星都在《推特》分享胸罩美乳照讓大家眼睛吃冰淇淋。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190213/640_ef3030324012ad02a55f6bf5ea9a57be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190213%2F640_ef3030324012ad02a55f6bf5ea9a57be.jpg&h=1b327e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自椎名香奈江推特<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190213/640_de358b2384e9ed9ddde6a0cb476f3363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190213%2F640_de358b2384e9ed9ddde6a0cb476f3363.jpg&h=fa4610c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自椎名香奈江推特<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190213/640_24d371609c89ded57c70ff3803602a4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190213%2F640_24d371609c89ded57c70ff3803602a4b.jpg&h=ad242fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻攝自雨宮留菜推特<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190213/640_beb88c4b11a16ab63ba64c3f8d98480b.jpg\" data-t